---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about State of Forms - Data Analytics and Engineering experts">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About State of Forms</h1>
      <p>Transforming data into competitive advantages since inception</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          We empower organizations to unlock the full potential of their data through 
          modern analytics, robust engineering, and production-ready solutions that drive 
          measurable business outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Do Section -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="text-center" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
        We bridge the gap between raw data and actionable insights
      </p>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>üéØ Data Analytics</h3>
          <p>
            We transform complex datasets into clear, actionable insights using advanced 
            statistical methods, machine learning, and visualization techniques.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üîß Data Engineering</h3>
          <p>
            We build scalable, reliable data infrastructure - from data lakes to warehouses, 
            ETL pipelines to real-time streaming architectures.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üíº Business Intelligence</h3>
          <p>
            We create intuitive dashboards and reporting systems that give stakeholders 
            the insights they need, when they need them.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üöÄ Custom Development</h3>
          <p>
            We develop full-stack analytics platforms tailored to your specific business 
            requirements and industry needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="text-center" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
        Quality, scalability, and client success drive everything we do
      </p>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>üéì Expertise-Driven</h3>
          <p>
            We leverage years of hands-on experience with production systems, big data 
            ecosystems, and modern development practices to deliver solutions that work 
            in real-world conditions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üß™ Quality-Focused</h3>
          <p>
            Every solution includes comprehensive unit testing, CI/CD pipelines, and 
            detailed documentation. We don't just build features - we build reliable systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>üìà Scalability First</h3>
          <p>
            Our architectures are designed to grow with your business. From prototype to 
            enterprise scale, we build foundations that support long-term success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>ü§ù Client Partnership</h3>
          <p>
            We work closely with clients to understand their unique challenges and goals. 
            Your success is our success, and we're committed to delivering value.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technology Expertise Section -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Our Technology Stack</h2>
      <p class="text-center" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
